{"tid":1396621,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"劇透！睇完 狂野時速：雙雄聯盟 既同我入黎","createTime":"2019-08-02T07:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T02:37:14.000Z","uid":296595,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b300b4353d632c635b9eda9001628803fa7706c8","tid":1396621,"uid":296595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:05:00.000Z","msg":"本身係F&amp;F迷，尋日一上就狗衝去睇，結果... 都未算失望嘅~<br />\n早已知呢套係外傳，內容同之前個8集係完全冇關係，無得駁故；<br />\n睇今次個Cast都估到係打、打同打；<br />\n但最估唔到係竟然有Ryan Reynolds，小弟認為係最大亮點，加唔少分；<br />\n呢套由Deadpool 導演主理，加咗好多笑位，The Rock同Jason Statham互串都好笑，總算係有D新元素；<br />\n同埋最尾有成3個彩蛋，有驚喜算幾有誠意<br />\n<br />\nP.S 有無人知deadpool 係咪有份拍ff9<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i4Ytrps.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi4Ytrps.png&h=02810af9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7f6cf1fd6cb62fcfc00440b55dae6030390ea4d","tid":1396621,"uid":77788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:17:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc370013f73382e71751e2ebf76d3b8949b2e7ef","tid":1396621,"uid":198133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7f6cf1fd6cb62fcfc00440b55dae6030390ea4d","tid":1396621,"uid":77788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:17:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:17:58.000Z","msg":"你當睇美國隊長既話好好睇"},{"pid":"ad6da1c97ae68713b8ae7f9eadb4e90063986768","tid":1396621,"uid":257021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc370013f73382e71751e2ebf76d3b8949b2e7ef","tid":1396621,"uid":198133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7f6cf1fd6cb62fcfc00440b55dae6030390ea4d","tid":1396621,"uid":77788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:17:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:17:58.000Z","msg":"你當睇美國隊長既話好好睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:20:39.000Z","msg":"The Rock<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/